Package tr.edu.bilkent.cs.patoh

Class Summary
HyperGraph Base class to issue HyperGraph operations: partitioning, reading from, writing to file, etc.
Partitioning Result storage class after partitioning a HyperGraph instance.
PartitioningParameters Java equivalent of PaToH_Parameters, and simply extending this class (probably) won't work -- try to use spare fields (allargs, inputfilename, etc.) instead.
 

Exception Summary
HyperGraphException Exception raised in case of a shared library related execution error.
